<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/pagbook.css">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .mainContainer {
            width: 100%; 
            height: auto; 
            margin: auto;
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            padding: 10px; 
        }

        .imageContainer {
            background-color: greenyellow;
            width: 400px;
            height: 500px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-right: 20px; 
        }

        .imageContainer img {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 100%;
            border: 1px solid black;
            border-radius: 15%;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .bookInfoContainer {
            width: 700px;
            height: 500px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .bookInfoChild {
            width: 70%;
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .bookInfoChild p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .bookInfoChild3 p {
            text-align: justify;
            padding: 0 50px;
        }

        .bookInfoChild4_SubItems {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        #stockNumber {
            border: 1px solid black;
            border-radius: 25%;
            width: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-left: 10px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .bookInfoChild5 {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
        }

        #cartBtn,
        #buyNowBtn {
            border: 1px solid black;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 190px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        #cartBtn {
            background-color: #FDBF0F;
        }

        #buyNowBtn {
            background-color: #F9784B;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: black;
            padding: 5px;
        }

        #authorContainer,  #synopsisContainer{
            border: 2px dotted black;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 6px #676767;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        #titleContainer {
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }

        #titleContainer img{
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        
        #priceStockContainer {
            font-size: 1.3em;
        }

        .stockBtn {
            background: none;
            color: inherit;
            border: none;
            padding: 0;
            padding-left: 6px;
            padding-right: 6px;
            font: inherit;
            cursor: pointer;
            outline: inherit;
            border: 1px solid black;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .mainContainer {
                flex-direction: column; 
            }

            .imageContainer {
                width: 100%; 
                height: auto; 
                margin-right: 0; 
                margin-bottom: 20px; 

            }

            .bookInfoContainer {
                width: 100%; 
                height: auto; 
            }

            .bookInfoChild {
                width: 100%; 
                margin-top: 10px;
                flex-direction: column; 
            }

            .bookInfoChild3 p {
                padding: 0 20px;
            }

            .bookInfoChild4_SubItems {
                flex-direction: column; 
                margin-top: 10px; 
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <%-
        include(navbar)
        %>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="mainContainer">
            <div class="imageContainer">
            </div>
            <div class="bookInfoContainer">
                <div id="titleContainer" class="bookInfoChild">
                    <p>Book Title</p>
                    <a href=""><img src="/images/favorite.svg" alt="Favorite Icon"></a>
                </div>
                <div id="authorContainer" class="bookInfoChild">
                    <p>Author Name</p>
                    <p></p>
                </div>
                <div id="synopsisContainer" class="bookInfoChild">
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Debitis repudiandae voluptates voluptatibus hic officiis vitae nisi vel officia neque esse architecto, incidunt eaque nulla harum quibusdam odio? Unde, laboriosam nobis.</p>
                </div>
                <div id="priceStockContainer" class="bookInfoChild">
                    <p>R$ 30.00</p>
                    <div class="bookInfoChild4_SubItems">
                        <button class="stockBtn">-</button>
                        <p id="stockNumber">1</p>
                        <button class="stockBtn">+</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bookInfoChild">
                    <a href="#" id="cartBtn"><img src="/images/SHOPPING_CART _Black.svg" alt="Shopping Cart"></a>
                    <a href="#" id="buyNowBtn">Buy Now</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
